The BCIE annual educational fair is back and this time it is happening face to face. The British Canadian International Education (BCIE) annual educational fair is a fantastic opportunity for students to meet with universities from the UK, USA and Australia. Students will learn about different study options available to them. This year’s event will be held in Lagos, Nigeria on Saturday, May 28th, 2022 at Sheraton Hotel Ikeja  and Abuja, Nigeria on Monday, May 30th, 2022 at Sheraton Hotel, Abuja. Here’s what you need to know about the BCIE fair! So come on down and chat with us about your options. International delegates from UK, USA and Australia universities will be live at the fair ground This year’s event will feature representatives from top universities in the UK, USA and Australia. Students will have the chance to ask questions about the admissions process, financial aid, information on scholarships and funding and student life at these institutions. This is a rare opportunity to get first-hand information about some of the most prestigious universities in the world, Attendees will also have the opportunity to learn more about BCIE’s services and how we can help you with your university application process. Programs and Schools This year’s annual educational fair is for those seeking admission as Undergraduates, Postgraduates or PhD into UK, USA and Australia,  Universities attending are;   Best Bulk SMS Provider in Kenya     Get your PVC ready!     5 Reasons You Need Travel Insurance   For more information https://bcie.co.uk//bcie-edufair-may-2022 BCIE offers 100 percent Customer Satisfaction, Visa success, and Student reward.  Come with your academic documents for on spot free application. The Event/Fair is totally free  To register for the event,  visit  for Abuja: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/341246757237 for Lagos: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/339381658677